txt_content:
没图, 仅提供怎么在IDE加载插件

首先, clone https://github.com/Karlatemp/NukkitLauncher 这个仓库并进行编译.
- MXLib - Unsafe - https://github.com/Karlatemp/MXB ... b.common.unsafe.jar
- JetBrains Annotations - http://mvnrepository.com
- Nukkit - ?
然后在你的Test source里创建类, 使用以下内容.
public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException, NoSuchFieldException {
        String project = "G:/IDEAProjects/PlaceholderAPI-Nukkit";
        String working = project + "/server";
        System.setProperty("user.dir", working);

        ResourceFinder finder = new ClassLoaderFinder(ClassLoader.getSystemClassLoader());
        ClassLoader loader = ClassLoader.getSystemClassLoader();
        NukkitBootstrap.bootstrap(finder, loader, loader,
                new File(working, "plugins/<Your Plugin Name>.jar"));
        Nukkit.main(args);
    }复制代码
如果你不想让logging出现错误的话, 在IDE的程序启动选项里改工作目录

        String working = ".";


        ResourceFinder finder = new ClassLoaderFinder(ClassLoader.getSystemClassLoader());
        ClassLoader loader = ClassLoader.getSystemClassLoader();
        NukkitBootstrap.bootstrap(finder, loader, loader,
                new File(working, "plugins/<Your Plugin Name>.jar"));
        Nukkit.main(args);

复制代码
好了, 都已经在IDE里启动了, 怎么调试就简单了, 这里不提. 不需要打包成jar就能加载插件. 实现原理自己看源码
